div.p: D85/9971, unit 130, VPRS 3992/P inward registered correspondence, VA 475 Chief Secretary's Department, Public Record Office, Victoria.

note.p: MS written by G. Luehmann and signed by M.

Estimates for three periods during the Quarter ending December 1885 were requested in H. Moors to M, 21 September 1885 (in this edition as 85-09-21d). The other estimates are for the whole quarter, M to G. Berry, 23 September1885 and October, M to G. Berry, 22 September 1885.

div.p: To the Honorable the Chief Secretary

I have the honor to submit for approval the following Estimate* of Expenditure during the two months
two months above Quarter struck through .
ending 30thNovember 1885.
